item.title: About
item.description: About Me I architect, implement, administer and troubleshoot servers, network, storage and infrastructure devices local and cloud-based interested in DevSecOps. I write about things I am familiar with, things I am learning, and the things that I have had to understand in order to help others understand. For more details on work experience, certifications and such, check LinkedIn. I tend to update that more frequently than this page. GitHub Stats
